[![hexagon setup example](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11464844/141402773-2fa1e859-cbe7-43a2-87e8-81620307167f.gif)](https://asciinema.org/a/Mk8of7EC0grfsSgWYrEdGCjdF)

